data.description: Welcome to this charming and meticulously renovated home nestled in a serene and quiet neighborhood, just a stone's throw away from local schools. This delightful residence exudes warmth, character, and timeless appeal. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by an open and bright living space that seamlessly connects the living and dining areas. Large windows allow natural light to flood the room, highlighting the gleaming new floors and freshly painted walls. This home offers three bedrooms, each with its own unique charm and a huge screened in porch off the dining area perfect for a relaxing evening! Hurry and schedule your own private tour today!
